extends ../_docs-template

block vars
  - var title = 'Tools Reference | Framework7 MCP Server';

block docs-index

block content
  .docs-nav
    include ../_docs-menu-mcp
  .docs-content

    h1 Tools Reference

    p The Framework7 MCP server provides 9 tools for querying Framework7 API documentation.

    h2 list-components

    p List all available Framework7 components and modules with their names.

    h4 Parameters

    p None.

    h4 Example

    ```json
      {
        "jsonrpc": "2.0",
        "id": 1,
        "method": "tools/call",
        "params": {
          "name": "list-components",
          "arguments": {}
        }
      }
    ```

    h2 get-component

    p Get the full API for a Framework7 component including parameters, events, methods, app methods, app parameters, app events, DOM events, and CSS variables.

    h4 Parameters

    table
      thead
        tr
          th Parameter
          th Type
          th Required
          th Description
      tbody
        tr
          td <code>name</code>
          td string
          td Yes
          td Component name. Accepts kebab-case (e.g., <code>smart-select</code>) or PascalCase (e.g., <code>SmartSelect</code>).

    h4 Example

    ```json
      {
        "jsonrpc": "2.0",
        "id": 1,
        "method": "tools/call",
        "params": {
          "name": "get-component",
          "arguments": {
            "name": "dialog"
          }
        }
      }
    ```

    h2 search-api

    p Search Framework7 API documentation across parameters, methods, events, and CSS variables. Returns matching results with descriptions.

    h4 Parameters

    table
      thead
        tr
          th Parameter
          th Type
          th Required
          th Description
      tbody
        tr
          td <code>query</code>
          td string
          td Yes
          td Search query string.
        tr
          td <code>type</code>
          td string
          td No
          td Filter by type. One of: <code>parameter</code>, <code>method</code>, <code>event</code>, <code>css-variable</code>, <code>all</code>. Defaults to <code>all</code>.

    h4 Example

    ```json
      {
        "jsonrpc": "2.0",
        "id": 1,
        "method": "tools/call",
        "params": {
          "name": "search-api",
          "arguments": {
            "query": "backdrop",
            "type": "parameter"
          }
        }
      }
    ```

    h2 get-parameter

    p Get detailed information about a specific Framework7 parameter/option by name, including type, default value, and description.

    h4 Parameters

    table
      thead
        tr
          th Parameter
          th Type
          th Required
          th Description
      tbody
        tr
          td <code>name</code>
          td string
          td Yes
          td The parameter name (e.g., <code>backdrop</code>, <code>animate</code>, <code>closeByBackdropClick</code>).
        tr
          td <code>component</code>
          td string
          td No
          td Component name to scope the search (e.g., <code>dialog</code>, <code>popup</code>).

    h4 Example

    ```json
      {
        "jsonrpc": "2.0",
        "id": 1,
        "method": "tools/call",
        "params": {
          "name": "get-parameter",
          "arguments": {
            "name": "closeByBackdropClick",
            "component": "dialog"
          }
        }
      }
    ```

    h2 get-method

    p Get detailed information about a specific Framework7 method by name, including signature, parameters, and description. Covers both instance methods and app-level methods.

    h4 Parameters

    table
      thead
        tr
          th Parameter
          th Type
          th Required
          th Description
      tbody
        tr
          td <code>name</code>
          td string
          td Yes
          td The method name (e.g., <code>open</code>, <code>close</code>, <code>create</code>, <code>destroy</code>).
        tr
          td <code>component</code>
          td string
          td No
          td Component name to scope the search (e.g., <code>dialog</code>, <code>popup</code>).

    h4 Example

    ```json
      {
        "jsonrpc": "2.0",
        "id": 1,
        "method": "tools/call",
        "params": {
          "name": "get-method",
          "arguments": {
            "name": "open",
            "component": "popup"
          }
        }
      }
    ```

    h2 get-event

    p Get detailed information about a specific Framework7 event by name, including parameters and description. Covers instance events, app-level events, and DOM events.

    h4 Parameters

    table
      thead
        tr
          th Parameter
          th Type
          th Required
          th Description
      tbody
        tr
          td <code>name</code>
          td string
          td Yes
          td The event name (e.g., <code>open</code>, <code>opened</code>, <code>close</code>, <code>closed</code>).
        tr
          td <code>component</code>
          td string
          td No
          td Component name to scope the search (e.g., <code>dialog</code>, <code>popup</code>).

    h4 Example

    ```json
      {
        "jsonrpc": "2.0",
        "id": 1,
        "method": "tools/call",
        "params": {
          "name": "get-event",
          "arguments": {
            "name": "opened",
            "component": "dialog"
          }
        }
      }
    ```

    h2 get-css-variables

    p Get CSS custom properties (variables) for a Framework7 component, grouped by theme (iOS, Material Design) with their values.

    h4 Parameters

    table
      thead
        tr
          th Parameter
          th Type
          th Required
          th Description
      tbody
        tr
          td <code>component</code>
          td string
          td Yes
          td Component name (e.g., <code>dialog</code>, <code>navbar</code>, <code>toolbar</code>).

    h4 Example

    ```json
      {
        "jsonrpc": "2.0",
        "id": 1,
        "method": "tools/call",
        "params": {
          "name": "get-css-variables",
          "arguments": {
            "component": "navbar"
          }
        }
      }
    ```

    h2 list-demos

    p List all available Framework7 demos with their slugs and available frameworks (core, vue, react, svelte).

    h4 Parameters

    p None.

    h4 Example

    ```json
      {
        "jsonrpc": "2.0",
        "id": 1,
        "method": "tools/call",
        "params": {
          "name": "list-demos",
          "arguments": {}
        }
      }
    ```

    h2 get-demo

    p Get demo source code for a specific Framework7 demo in a given framework variant (core, vue, react, or svelte).

    h4 Parameters

    table
      thead
        tr
          th Parameter
          th Type
          th Required
          th Description
      tbody
        tr
          td <code>slug</code>
          td string
          td Yes
          td The demo slug (e.g., <code>accordion</code>, <code>action-sheet</code>, <code>color-themes</code>). Use <code>list-demos</code> to get available slugs.
        tr
          td <code>framework</code>
          td string
          td Yes
          td Framework variant. One of: <code>core</code>, <code>vue</code>, <code>react</code>, <code>svelte</code>.

    h4 Example

    ```json
      {
        "jsonrpc": "2.0",
        "id": 1,
        "method": "tools/call",
        "params": {
          "name": "get-demo",
          "arguments": {
            "slug": "color-themes",
            "framework": "core"
          }
        }
      }
    ```

